Class JarFileEntry

java.lang.Object
  de.wwu.muggl.ui.gui.support.JarFileEntry

public class JarFileEntry
extends java.lang.Object

Representation for a entry in a jar file. This supporting class is needed to display jar files in the directory tree and get means of expanding them.

Version:
1.0.0, 2010-03-16
Author:
Tim Majchrzak
